Project Bureau — ATF1502AS Logic Block B Macrocells

Project Bureau aims at documenting the bitstream format of Microchip ATF15xx CPLDs. This is a work in progress. See more in the repository

Macrocell Configuration Bitmap

Logic block B uses 320 (known) fuses within range 15360..16320 for macrocells MC17, MC18, MC19, MC20, MC21, MC22, MC23, MC24, MC25, MC26, MC27, MC28, MC29, MC30, MC31, MC32.
